WEBVTT

00:00.091 --> 00:02.714
ï»¿In order to make your language learning a lot more fun,...

00:02.921 --> 00:05.309
...then you should focus on the things that interest you the most.

00:05.505 --> 00:08.004
If you want to learn the language to learn more about the culture,...

00:08.167 --> 00:09.883
...then you should be watching films,...

00:09.986 --> 00:13.576
...you should be reading and enjoying those things that are available.

00:14.086 --> 00:18.591
It's also important to reward yourself for the learning that you're doing,...

00:18.690 --> 00:20.649
...so make sure that you give yourself little treats...

00:20.752 --> 00:23.811
...and maybe even plan a holiday or trip to...

00:24.350 --> 00:25.548
...the country where they speak the language...

00:25.625 --> 00:29.366
...so you can actually see how much progress you've made since you started learning...

00:29.441 --> 00:32.763
...and how far you could still come in a similar amount of time.

